d,\nwe use the previous results together to provide the canonical and refined\nactive bijections alluded to above. We also give an overview and examples of\nthe various results of independent interest involved in the construction. They\narise as soon as the ground set of an oriented matroid is linearly ordered.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Jul 2018 17:41:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 18 Jul 2018 12:51:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-19"}
