hat can help dynamically eliminate the\ndomains producing the negative baryon asymmetry. It is found that this can be\nachieved by a tiny explicit $CP$-violating phase of ${\\cal O}(10^{-15})$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Jul 2018 15:06:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-26"}
