-of-the art $N$-body simulations of the co-evolution of MPs in globular\nclusters that include the effect of binaries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Jul 2018 19:09:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-05"}
